        </a>
      </div>
      <div>
        Hi, I'm <strong>Bastian García Pérez</strong>
        <br />
        <br />
        A web developer specializing in backend services with Spring Boot and HTML,
        CSS, Angular, Typescript, Firebase, and more.
        <br />
        <br />
        I'm passionate about learning new techs and experiences. Feel free to navigate
        over the web to know me better and don't doubt to ask me anything if you
        want to!
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
   @keyframes slide-from-left {
    from {
      
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-100%);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-left-opacity {
    animation: slide-from-left 1.0s ease-in-out forwards;
  }

  .instructions {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 25%);
    background: #3aafa9;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: justify;
  }
</style>
